Name: Average time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and SW-Checklist Completed across all variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time it takes for SW-Checklist Completed to occur after Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Average time until SW-Checklist Completed is performed in variants that include Plagiarism Originality Report Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Checklist Completed in cases where the checklist completion was delayed (e.g., preceded by 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' or 'SW-Checklist Completion now due')
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and the end of case where activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days occurs

Name: Time from Manuscript Export Succeeded to SW-Checklist Completed in submissions that eventually lead to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Elapsed time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-Checklist Completed in high-performance versus low-performance variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Average time for SW-Checklist Completed when followed directly by SW-Awaiting AE Assignment versus when followed by a checklist reminder activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Minimum time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and SW-Checklist Completed in variants that proceed to reviewer assignment without delays
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total time it takes SW-Checklist Completed to be done after the occurrence of Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Time until SW-Checklist Completed in variants that include Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded compared to those that do not
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Average time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Checklist Completed in cases that result in eventual acceptance (e.g., ending with RW-EIC Accept)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Cycle time of SW-Checklist Completed measured from case start (first event timestamp) to the timestamp of SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total time between SW-Checklist Completed and SW-Awaiting AE Assignment, highlighting downstream impact of checklist completion speed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Minimum time it takes for SW-Checklist Completed to occur in variants that avoid any checklist-related reminder activities
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'
